#: upstream/_versions/1.11/guides/getting-started-reactive.adoc:390
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"@GET\n"
"@Produces(MediaType.SERVER_SENT_EVENTS)\n"
"@RestSseElementType(MediaType.TEXT_PLAIN)\n"
"@Path(\"/stream/{count}/{name}\")\n"
